{"tid":1740288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反思檢討] 我哋而家需要嘅係休息一兩日回氣，然後再日日黎明行動","createTime":"2019-11-20T01:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:27:58.000Z","uid":67023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1f903726d09a20c6fd050c6d22b28c7291d37c","tid":1740288,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:35:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開宗明義講明非休息撚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解要回氣？<br />\n手足打咗咁多日，日日打到凌晨，仲未計有啲人第二日要返工，鐵人都攰啦<br />\n<br />\n而且啱啱經歷慘敗，大家都需要啲時間冷靜一下去反思。但係休息不宜過長，休太耐就會變咗休息成世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以一至兩日作為休整同重新部署係最為合適。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家唔好灰心，覺得輸咗一次就成場運動完咗，我哋已經再無退路，抗爭係一世嘅事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只爭春秋，不爭朝夕</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d3165fb988acc726b474c191c8d8e8e4cf20f058","tid":1740288,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:36:30.000Z","msg":"推幾下等有緣人睇到，睇唔到就算了"},{"pid":"79797fd916144301da12eef6ae3a25295c25d7a4","tid":1740288,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"記住每個人教要獨立思考，咁先可以好似AI咁不停自我學習"},{"pid":"e84d1e9dfce808f03ceb1011dcbdd3bc92e0aab7","tid":1740288,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"最後一推，香港人復仇"},{"pid":"356363cd1e62e39468b310a7252be2c6a738c465","tid":1740288,"uid":67023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:41:50.000Z","msg":"搵人應下我都好&hellip;"},{"pid":"2c6b262352918728d92f878893a94e5b11e56e8a","tid":1740288,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:42:20.000Z","msg":"18-8-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbf